These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, australian, american
1. the dutch is in an odd position##4
2. the american is between the brazilian and the dutch##2
3. the american is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | brazilian | american | dutch | australian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, garlic, mango, apple
1. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person eating apple##1
2. the person eating garlic is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | garlic | zucchini | apple | mango |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, sports, satire, western
1. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
2. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching western movies and the person watching sports movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | western | satire | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, water-polo, skiing, cricket
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person who's sport is handball##3
2. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is cricket is between the person who's sport is handball and the person who's sport is skiing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | water-polo | handball | cricket | skiing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, cycling, rowing, rugby
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | rugby | ice-hockey | rowing | cycling |

