.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, russian, spanish, pakistani
1. the russian is on the far right##1
2. the russian is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
3. the spanish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | spanish | french | pakistani | russian |

