.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, ambient, classical, metal
1. the fan of metal is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
2. the fan of soul is between the fan of ambient and the fan of classical##2
3. the fan of soul is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |  4   |
