.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, snowmobile, boat, bus
1. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |   2    |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | boat | snowmobile | bus | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, soy-milk, fanta
1. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking juice##2
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2     |  3   |   4   |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | soy-milk | juice | fanta |

