.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-14::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, handball, lacrosse, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | lacrosse | skateboarding | snowboarding | handball |

