.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, broccoli, cabbage, carrot
1. the person eating broccoli is the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person eating carrot is on the left or right of the person eating cabbage##3
3. the person eating cabbage is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating nectarine is in an even position##4
5. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | cabbage | carrot | broccoli | nectarine |

